flowchart TD
    A[main.py / compare_baselines.py] --> B[sim.config.load_config]
    B --> C[SimConfig]
    C --> D[sim.env.SimulationEnv]

    D --> E[sim.topology.TopologyModel]
    E --> F[sim.orbit - SGP4 optional]

    D --> G[env.export_state]
    G --> H[scheduler policy]
    H --> I[Action list]
    I --> D

    D --> J[Task arrivals and tile generation]
    D --> K[Apply actions: LOCAL/OFFLOAD/WAIT]
    D --> L[Advance transfers]
    D --> M[Advance compute]
    D --> N[Deadline and failure handling]
    D --> O[sim.metrics.Metrics]

    O --> P[summary JSON]
    P --> Q[metrics.json / stdout]
